You will be welcome to come a charge your car at my premises.

I just moved in a big house where I also host people who are on holiday or just want to spend some days relaxing in a peaceful and green garden.
I have three rooms to rent in a separate apartment and there is also parking space for your vehicle. 

I believe in green energy and sustainability, recycling and respecting the planet earth so I am trying to do all I can to offer green services on my premises.
